{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hard Glide is an experimental fast-paced arcade game with inertial mouse control only (but you can also use a gamepad or mouse+WASD). A small fragile bot has been awakened among the bizarre world of machines, driven by the commands of the mysterious Mainframe, he must overcome increasingly difficult levels filled with a variety of hostile bots and dangerous obstacles, and fulfill his main Goal. This is what his Program says. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/hardGlide3.gif?t=1739533913\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The controls in the game are a little unusual, but quite simple:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">move the mouse to control the movement of your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">press and hold down the left mouse button to shoot and lock the sight in one direction, regardless of the movement direction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">while shooting, you can rotate the sight on 180 degrees by pressing the right mouse button</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">transferring objects (keys) and moving platforms at transit stations also occurs by holding down the left mouse button </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">if you need a hint where the level goals are, just click on the middle mouse button (wheel)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/hardGlide7.gif?t=1739533913\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When creating this game, I was inspired by arcade games of the past, I tried to get closer to the same adrenaline-pumping gameplay experience, but with the addition of modern graphics and effects. The game is aimed at those players who love action games of dexterity and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/hardGlide6.gif?t=1739533913\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"nice start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/a9b2cc1523aa187e20e5723809f3ea35cd1701dd.jpg"},{"name":"self-confident","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/28585850442cc8da3167209b09317233ea386a73.jpg"},{"name":"first destruction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/9459132b36c292d3aabe635f6011b33b43624a8f.jpg"},{"name":"turn over","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/2a663e60c3a2e96fb478fac492535860bcd57e55.jpg"},{"name":"safe limiter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/8c0012801f898e970cb861424a65e8f87f8a6725.jpg"},{"name":"beast hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/a36c019ff1afb77db5368de810d1f2ab0a06a902.jpg"},{"name":"key keeper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/d72aebff301bf3215c1ae447c0f9d56883876aad.jpg"},{"name":"vulnerable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/a1332a64348e9f22e19b67a03d76f6b7eb101738.jpg"},{"name":"stubborn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/37896c8a51d702a501469b22d9ea3f1e8844750f.jpg"},{"name":"unstoppable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1731390/ce3f4018a6e78e54ce3f80585bcf6b3b87b4e40c.jpg"}],"total":91},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739533913","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/page